<SYNC START=977194><P CLASS=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC START=977395><P CLASS=KRCC>켄시로씨...!
<SYNC START=979570><P CLASS=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC START=991492><P CLASS=KRCC>바보 같은 남자다! 일부러 돌아오다니!
<SYNC START=995974><P CLASS=KRCC>&nbsp;
